 <h1><a class="anchor" id="cset"></a>
配置包源路径</h1>
<p>在.emacs文件或其他启动文件中输入如下脚本，配置使用package插件管理和包源路径</p>
<pre class="fragment">;; Added by Package.el.  This must come before configurations of
;; installed packages.  Don't delete this line.  If you don't want it,
;; just comment it out by adding a semicolon to the start of the line.
;; You may delete these explanatory comments.
(package-initialize)

;;; Also use Melpa for most packages
(add-to-list 'package-archives '("melpa" . "http://melpa.milkbox.net/packages/"))
(add-to-list 'package-archives '("melpa-stable" . "http://melpa-stable.milkbox.net/packages/"))

(setq package-archives '(("gnu"   . "http://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/elpa/gnu/")
                         ("tuna" . "http://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/elpa/melpa/")
                         ("melpa" . "http://melpa.milkbox.net/packages/")
                         ("melpa-stable" . "http://melpa-stable.milkbox.net/packages/")
             ("elpy" . "https://jorgenschaefer.github.io/packages/")
                          ("tuna-stable" . "http://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/elpa/melpa-stable/")))
</pre><p> 配置完成后运行M-X package-refresh-contents更新插件缓存记录 </p>
<h1><a class="anchor" id="use_smex"></a>
smex插件的使用</h1>
<p>插件可以帮助快速输入命令，使用工具包中的smex-master.zip或在https://github.com/nonsequitur/smex下载最新版本，解压后将smex.el放在emacs的加载路径上。或者直接使用M-X package-install [ret] smex [ret]，使用包管理器进行安装然后在.emacs文件中输入下面的代码：</p>
<pre class="fragment">(require 'smex) ; Not needed if you use package.el
(smex-initialize) ; Can be omitted. This might cause a (minimal) delay
                  ; when Smex is auto-initialized on its first run.
(global-set-key (kbd "M-x") 'smex)
(global-set-key (kbd "M-X") 'smex-major-mode-commands)
;; This is your old M-x.
(global-set-key (kbd "C-c C-c M-x") 'execute-extended-command)
</pre><p> 就可以完成对smex的支持，这时输入M-x就会看到提示信息 </p>
<h1><a class="anchor" id="ac"></a>
自动补全功能</h1>
<p>运行M-X package-install[ret] auto-complete[ret]进行安装，将下面的脚本输入.emacs后重启emacs，即可使用自动补全功能</p>
<pre class="fragment">(require 'auto-complete-config)
(add-to-list 'ac-dictionary-directories "~/.emacs.d/ac-dict")
(ac-config-default)
</pre> <h1><a class="anchor" id="pyac"></a>
支持python的自动补全功能</h1>
<ol type="1">
<li>升级python到2.7或以上版本，python2.6及较低版本不能正常使用pip 参考 <a href="centos_python.html">升级CentOS的Python到2.7 </a> 和 <a href="py_setting.html#ugsetpip">python设置</a></li>
<li>安装python依赖包 <pre class="fragment"># Either of these
pip install rope
pip install jedi
# flake8 用来检查语法错误
pip install flake8
# importmagic 用来自动引入需要的包
pip install importmagic
# autopep8 用来检查PEP8规范
pip install autopep8
# yapf 用来格式化代码
pip install yapf
</pre></li>
<li>如果包源中找不到elpy添加https://jorgenschaefer.github.io/packages/到包源中，在.emacs中添加 <pre class="fragment">(add-to-list 'package-archives
             '("elpy" . "https://jorgenschaefer.github.io/packages/"))
</pre></li>
<li>打开emacs运行 M-x package-refresh-contents加载新的库，然后运行M-x package-install RET elpy RET（RET即回车键）安装elpy</li>
<li>在.emacs中添加(elpy-enable)，启用elpy </li>
</ol>
